{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e67517a89e","title":"对军队文化大革命的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0f51b3fbbe","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":null,"articleId":"e67517a89e"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"6f7a683373","name":"军队和军事","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"dff8972b04","type":"title","text":"对军队文化大革命的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e67517a89e"},{"id":"d9fc0458c7","type":"paragraph","text":"对军队文化大革命的指示","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e67517a89e"},{"id":"a3daf8c94d","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e67517a89e"},{"id":"96a4d91c4f","type":"paragraph","text":"1967.01.00","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e67517a89e"},{"id":"c8f59290c0","type":"paragraph","text":"一、 我认为十三个军区不要同时搞，要有前有后。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e67517a89e"},{"id":"643729df8c","type":"paragraph","text":"二、 地方文化大革命正在猛烈开展，夺权斗争还在激烈进行，我们军队要支持地方革命左派进行夺权斗争，因此军队和地方文化大革命要叉开。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e67517a89e"},{"id":"b26549099b","type":"paragraph","text":"三、 现在国际上帝、修、反正在利用我们文化大革命继续大搞反华活动。如苏联在镇压学生，新疆边境飞机活动多了，地面部队也在调动。凡是前线的大军区部队要有警惕，要有所准备。如济南、南京、福州、广州、昆明军区。所以文化大革命的时间要稍推一下。将来一定要搞的，顾大局。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e67517a89e"}],"page":{"id":"2fdc2e7998","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"e67517a89e","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}